{
  "video_id": "q43uXdOKPD8",
  "title": "Shigeru Ban: Emergency shelters made from paper",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12359.0,
      "end_time": 14800.0,
      "text": "Hi. I am an architect."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14800.0,
      "end_time": 16456.0,
      "text": "I am the only architect in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16456.0,
      "end_time": 19772.0,
      "text": "making buildings out of paper like this cardboard tube,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19772.0,
      "end_time": 22337.0,
      "text": "and this exhibition is the first one I did"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22338.0,
      "end_time": 23846.0,
      "text": "using paper tubes."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23846.0,
      "end_time": 28271.0,
      "text": "1986, much, much longer before people started talking"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28271.0,
      "end_time": 32474.0,
      "text": "about ecological issues and environmental issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32473.0,
      "end_time": 35763.0,
      "text": "I just started testing the paper tube"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35764.0,
      "end_time": 38499.0,
      "text": "in order to use this as a building structure."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38499.0,
      "end_time": 43652.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very complicated to test the new material for the building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43652.0,
      "end_time": 46150.0,
      "text": "but this is much stronger than I expected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46150.0,
      "end_time": 48362.0,
      "text": "and also it&#39;s very easy to waterproof,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48362.0,
      "end_time": 50257.0,
      "text": "and also, because it&#39;s industrial material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50257.0,
      "end_time": 52960.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also possible to fireproof."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52960.0,
      "end_time": 56793.0,
      "text": "Then I built the temporary structure, 1990."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56793.0,
      "end_time": 59800.0,
      "text": "This is the first temporary building made out of paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59800.0,
      "end_time": 63870.0,
      "text": "There are 330 tubes, diameter 55 [centimeters],"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63870.0,
      "end_time": 65512.0,
      "text": "there are only 12 tubes with a diameter"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65512.0,
      "end_time": 68282.0,
      "text": "of 120 centimeters, or four feet, wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68282.0,
      "end_time": 70902.0,
      "text": "As you see it in the photo, inside is the toilet."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70902.0,
      "end_time": 73553.0,
      "text": "In case you&#39;re finished with toilet paper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73553.0,
      "end_time": 75872.0,
      "text": "you can tear off the inside of the wall. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75873.0,
      "end_time": 78265.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s very useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78265.0,
      "end_time": 82304.0,
      "text": "Year 2000, there was a big expo in Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82304.0,
      "end_time": 84923.0,
      "text": "I was asked to design the building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84923.0,
      "end_time": 87717.0,
      "text": "because the theme of the expo was environmental issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87717.0,
      "end_time": 92205.0,
      "text": "So I was chosen to build the pavilion out of paper tubes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 92205.0,
      "end_time": 93932.0,
      "text": "recyclable paper."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93932.0,
      "end_time": 96902.0,
      "text": "My goal of the design is not when it&#39;s completed."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96902.0,
      "end_time": 98986.0,
      "text": "My goal was when the building was demolished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98986.0,
      "end_time": 102962.0,
      "text": "because each country makes a lot of pavilions"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102962.0,
      "end_time": 106620.0,
      "text": "but after half a year, we create a lot of industrial waste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 106620.0,
      "end_time": 110743.0,
      "text": "so my building has to be reused or recycled."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 110743.0,
      "end_time": 112845.0,
      "text": "After, the building was recycled."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112846.0,
      "end_time": 115492.0,
      "text": "So that was the goal of my design."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 115492.0,
      "end_time": 118580.0,
      "text": "Then I was very lucky to win the competition"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118580.0,
      "end_time": 121238.0,
      "text": "to build the second Pompidou Center in France"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121238.0,
      "end_time": 122713.0,
      "text": "in the city of Metz."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122713.0,
      "end_time": 124208.0,
      "text": "Because I was so poor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124209.0,
      "end_time": 126376.0,
      "text": "I wanted to rent an office in Paris,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 126376.0,
      "end_time": 127893.0,
      "text": "but I couldn&#39;t afford it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 127893.0,
      "end_time": 129934.0,
      "text": "so I decided to bring my students to Paris"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129934.0,
      "end_time": 133450.0,
      "text": "to build our office on top of the Pompidou Center in Paris"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133450.0,
      "end_time": 134685.0,
      "text": "by ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134685.0,
      "end_time": 138140.0,
      "text": "So we brought the paper tubes and the wooden joints"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138140.0,
      "end_time": 142990.0,
      "text": "to complete the 35-meter-long office."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142990.0,
      "end_time": 145132.0,
      "text": "We stayed there for six years without paying any rent."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145133.0,
      "end_time": 149400.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149400.0,
      "end_time": 151391.0,
      "text": "Thank you. I had one big problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 151391.0,
      "end_time": 153745.0,
      "text": "Because we were part of the exhibition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 153745.0,
      "end_time": 157490.0,
      "text": "even if my friend wanted to see me, they had to buy a ticket to see me."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 157490.0,
      "end_time": 159252.0,
      "text": "That was the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159252.0,
      "end_time": 162200.0,
      "text": "Then I completed the Pompidou Center in Metz."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162200.0,
      "end_time": 163974.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a very popular museum now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 163974.0,
      "end_time": 167140.0,
      "text": "and I created a big monument for the government."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167140.0,
      "end_time": 169390.0,
      "text": "But then I was very disappointed"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169390.0,
      "end_time": 171635.0,
      "text": "at my profession as an architect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171635.0,
      "end_time": 175662.0,
      "text": "because we are not helping, we are not working for society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175663.0,
      "end_time": 178907.0,
      "text": "but we are working for privileged people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178907.0,
      "end_time": 182990.0,
      "text": "rich people, government, developers."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 182990.0,
      "end_time": 184619.0,
      "text": "They have money and power."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 184619.0,
      "end_time": 186416.0,
      "text": "Those are invisible."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186416.0,
      "end_time": 190244.0,
      "text": "So they hire us to visualize their power and money"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 190244.0,
      "end_time": 192462.0,
      "text": "by making monumental architecture."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 192477.0,
      "end_time": 194642.0,
      "text": "That is our profession, even historically it&#39;s the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 194642.0,
      "end_time": 196994.0,
      "text": "even now we are doing the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 196994.0,
      "end_time": 200318.0,
      "text": "So I was very disappointed that we are not working for society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200318.0,
      "end_time": 204305.0,
      "text": "even though there are so many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 204320.0,
      "end_time": 207212.0,
      "text": "who lost their houses by natural disasters."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 207212.0,
      "end_time": 210255.0,
      "text": "But I must say they are no longer natural disasters."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 210255.0,
      "end_time": 213240.0,
      "text": "For example, earthquakes never kill people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 213240.0,
      "end_time": 215413.0,
      "text": "but collapse of the buildings kill people."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 215413.0,
      "end_time": 217453.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the responsibility of architects."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 217453.0,
      "end_time": 219190.0,
      "text": "Then people need some temporary housing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 219190.0,
      "end_time": 220852.0,
      "text": "but there are no architects working there"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 220852.0,
      "end_time": 224512.0,
      "text": "because we are too busy working for privileged people."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 224512.0,
      "end_time": 228391.0,
      "text": "So I thought, even as architects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 228391.0,
      "end_time": 233147.0,
      "text": "we can be involved in the reconstruction of temporary housing."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 233147.0,
      "end_time": 234939.0,
      "text": "We can make it better."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 234939.0,
      "end_time": 238971.0,
      "text": "So that is why I started working in disaster areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 238972.0,
      "end_time": 242698.0,
      "text": "1994, there was a big disaster in Rwanda, Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 242698.0,
      "end_time": 245430.0,
      "text": "Two tribes, Hutu and Tutsi, fought each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 245430.0,
      "end_time": 247928.0,
      "text": "Over two million people became refugees."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 247928.0,
      "end_time": 251679.0,
      "text": "But I was so surprised to see the shelter, refugee camp"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 251679.0,
      "end_time": 253913.0,
      "text": "organized by the U.N."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 253913.0,
      "end_time": 257207.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re so poor, and they are freezing"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 257207.0,
      "end_time": 259329.0,
      "text": "with blankets during the rainy season,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 259329.0,
      "end_time": 262840.0,
      "text": "In the shelters built by the U.N.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 262840.0,
      "end_time": 264390.0,
      "text": "they were just providing a plastic sheet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 264391.0,
      "end_time": 268540.0,
      "text": "and the refugees had to cut the trees, and just like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 268540.0,
      "end_time": 270306.0,
      "text": "But over two million people cut trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 270306.0,
      "end_time": 273970.0,
      "text": "It just became big, heavy deforestation"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 273970.0,
      "end_time": 274830.0,
      "text": "and an environmental problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 274830.0,
      "end_time": 278600.0,
      "text": "That is why they started providing aluminum pipes, aluminum barracks."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 278600.0,
      "end_time": 280347.0,
      "text": "Very expensive, they throw them out for money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 280347.0,
      "end_time": 282272.0,
      "text": "then cutting trees again."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 282273.0,
      "end_time": 286294.0,
      "text": "So I proposed my idea to improve the situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 286294.0,
      "end_time": 288454.0,
      "text": "using these recycled paper tubes"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 288454.0,
      "end_time": 291387.0,
      "text": "because this is so cheap and also so strong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 291387.0,
      "end_time": 294134.0,
      "text": "but my budget is only 50 U.S. dollars per unit."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 294134.0,
      "end_time": 297950.0,
      "text": "We built 50 units to do that as a monitoring test"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 297950.0,
      "end_time": 302801.0,
      "text": "for the durability and moisture and termites, so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 302801.0,
      "end_time": 307381.0,
      "text": "And then, year afterward, 1995, in Kobe, Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 307381.0,
      "end_time": 309174.0,
      "text": "we had a big earthquake."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 309174.0,
      "end_time": 311686.0,
      "text": "Nearly 7,000 people were killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 311686.0,
      "end_time": 314676.0,
      "text": "and the city like this Nagata district,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 314677.0,
      "end_time": 317995.0,
      "text": "all the city was burned in a fire after the earthquake."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 317995.0,
      "end_time": 321936.0,
      "text": "And also I found out there&#39;s many Vietnamese refugees"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 321936.0,
      "end_time": 324531.0,
      "text": "suffering and gathering at a Catholic church --"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 324531.0,
      "end_time": 326450.0,
      "text": "all the building was totally destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 326450.0,
      "end_time": 329950.0,
      "text": "So I went there and also I proposed to the priests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 329951.0,
      "end_time": 332569.0,
      "text": "\"Why don&#39;t we rebuild the church out of paper tubes?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 332569.0,
      "end_time": 335709.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Oh God, are you crazy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 335709.0,
      "end_time": 337818.0,
      "text": "After a fire, what are you proposing?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 337818.0,
      "end_time": 341445.0,
      "text": "So he never trusted me, but I didn&#39;t give up."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 341446.0,
      "end_time": 343328.0,
      "text": "I started commuting to Kobe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 343328.0,
      "end_time": 345957.0,
      "text": "and I met the society of Vietnamese people."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 345957.0,
      "end_time": 348623.0,
      "text": "They were living like this with very poor plastic sheets"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 348624.0,
      "end_time": 349905.0,
      "text": "in the park."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 349905.0,
      "end_time": 353147.0,
      "text": "So I proposed to rebuild. I raised -- did fundraising."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 353147.0,
      "end_time": 355703.0,
      "text": "I made a paper tube shelter for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 355703.0,
      "end_time": 358661.0,
      "text": "and in order to make it easy to be built by students"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 358661.0,
      "end_time": 360244.0,
      "text": "and also easy to demolish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 360244.0,
      "end_time": 363453.0,
      "text": "I used beer crates as a foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 363453.0,
      "end_time": 366420.0,
      "text": "I asked the Kirin beer company to propose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 366430.0,
      "end_time": 368763.0,
      "text": "because at that time, the Asahi beer company"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 368763.0,
      "end_time": 370775.0,
      "text": "made their plastic beer crates red,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 370775.0,
      "end_time": 373188.0,
      "text": "which doesn&#39;t go with the color of the paper tubes."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 373189.0,
      "end_time": 375507.0,
      "text": "The color coordination is very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 375507.0,
      "end_time": 378700.0,
      "text": "And also I still remember, we were expecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 378700.0,
      "end_time": 381550.0,
      "text": "to have a beer inside the plastic beer crate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 381550.0,
      "end_time": 382949.0,
      "text": "but it came empty. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 382949.0,
      "end_time": 386341.0,
      "text": "So I remember it was so disappointing."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 386341.0,
      "end_time": 388579.0,
      "text": "So during the summer with my students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 388579.0,
      "end_time": 390765.0,
      "text": "we built over 50 units of the shelters."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 390765.0,
      "end_time": 393536.0,
      "text": "Finally the priest, finally he trusted me to rebuild."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 393536.0,
      "end_time": 395827.0,
      "text": "He said, \"As long as you collect money by yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 395827.0,
      "end_time": 398810.0,
      "text": "bring your students to build, you can do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 398810.0,
      "end_time": 400564.0,
      "text": "So we spent five weeks rebuilding the church."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 400564.0,
      "end_time": 404620.0,
      "text": "It was meant to stay there for three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 404620.0,
      "end_time": 407360.0,
      "text": "but actually it stayed there 10 years because people loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 407360.0,
      "end_time": 411169.0,
      "text": "Then, in Taiwan, they had a big earthquake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 411169.0,
      "end_time": 415119.0,
      "text": "and we proposed to donate this church,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 415119.0,
      "end_time": 416720.0,
      "text": "so we dismantled them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 416720.0,
      "end_time": 418965.0,
      "text": "we sent them over to be built by volunteer people."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 418965.0,
      "end_time": 422589.0,
      "text": "It stayed there in Taiwan as a permanent church even now."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 422589.0,
      "end_time": 425800.0,
      "text": "So this building became a permanent building."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 425800.0,
      "end_time": 429729.0,
      "text": "Then I wonder, what is a permanent and what is a temporary building?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 429729.0,
      "end_time": 431662.0,
      "text": "Even a building made in paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 431662.0,
      "end_time": 435191.0,
      "text": "can be permanent as long as people love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 435192.0,
      "end_time": 437488.0,
      "text": "Even a concrete building can be very temporary"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 437488.0,
      "end_time": 439505.0,
      "text": "if that is made to make money."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 439505.0,
      "end_time": 442215.0,
      "text": "In 1999, in Turkey, the big earthquake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 442215.0,
      "end_time": 446364.0,
      "text": "I went there to use the local material to build a shelter."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 446365.0,
      "end_time": 450219.0,
      "text": "2001, in West India, I built also a shelter."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 450219.0,
      "end_time": 454300.0,
      "text": "In 2004, in Sri Lanka, after the Sumatra earthquake"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 454300.0,
      "end_time": 457981.0,
      "text": "and tsunami, I rebuilt Islamic fishermen&#39;s villages."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 457981.0,
      "end_time": 463432.0,
      "text": "And in 2008, in Chengdu, Sichuan area in China,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 463432.0,
      "end_time": 466358.0,
      "text": "nearly 70,000 people were killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 466358.0,
      "end_time": 469443.0,
      "text": "and also especially many of the schools were destroyed"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 469443.0,
      "end_time": 472893.0,
      "text": "because of the corruption between the authority and the contractor."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 472893.0,
      "end_time": 475861.0,
      "text": "I was asked to rebuild the temporary church."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 475861.0,
      "end_time": 479647.0,
      "text": "I brought my Japanese students to work with the Chinese students."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 479647.0,
      "end_time": 482508.0,
      "text": "In one month, we completed nine classrooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 482508.0,
      "end_time": 484159.0,
      "text": "over 500 square meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 484160.0,
      "end_time": 488632.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s still used, even after the current earthquake in China."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 488632.0,
      "end_time": 494960.0,
      "text": "In 2009, in Italy, L&#39;Aquila, also they had a big earthquake."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 494960.0,
      "end_time": 496448.0,
      "text": "And this is a very interesting photo:"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 496448.0,
      "end_time": 499164.0,
      "text": "former Prime Minister Berlusconi"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 499165.0,
      "end_time": 503583.0,
      "text": "and Japanese former former former former Prime Minister Mr. Aso --"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 503583.0,
      "end_time": 507464.0,
      "text": "you know, because we have to change the prime minister ever year."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 507464.0,
      "end_time": 512426.0,
      "text": "And they are very kind, affording my model."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 512426.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516825.00000000006,
      "text": "I proposed a big rebuilding, a temporary music hall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 516825.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519269.00000000006,
      "text": "because L&#39;Aquila is very famous for music"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 519269.0,
      "end_time": 520693.0,
      "text": "and all the concert halls were destroyed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 520693.0,
      "end_time": 522825.0,
      "text": "so musicians were moving out."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 522826.0,
      "end_time": 524253.0,
      "text": "So I proposed to the mayor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 524253.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526488.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to rebuild the temporary auditorium."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 526488.0,
      "end_time": 529434.0,
      "text": "He said, \"As long as you bring your money, you can do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 529434.0,
      "end_time": 530617.0,
      "text": "And I was very lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 530617.0,
      "end_time": 532918.0,
      "text": "Mr. Berlusconi brought G8 summit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 532918.0,
      "end_time": 535240.0,
      "text": "and our former prime minister came,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 535240.0,
      "end_time": 538229.0,
      "text": "so they helped us to collect money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 538229.0,
      "end_time": 541720.0,
      "text": "and I got half a million euros from the Japanese government"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 541720.0,
      "end_time": 543959.0,
      "text": "to rebuild this temporary auditorium."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 543959.0,
      "end_time": 548679.0,
      "text": "Year 2010 in Haiti, there was a big earthquake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 548679.0,
      "end_time": 550270.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s impossible to fly over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 550270.0,
      "end_time": 553287.0,
      "text": "so I went to Santo Domingo, next-door country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 553287.0,
      "end_time": 556202.0,
      "text": "to drive six hours to get to Haiti"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 556202.0,
      "end_time": 559493.0,
      "text": "with the local students in Santo Domingo"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 559493.0,
      "end_time": 562946.0,
      "text": "to build 50 units of shelter out of local paper tubes."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 562946.0,
      "end_time": 566559.0,
      "text": "This is what happened in Japan two years ago, in northern Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 566559.0,
      "end_time": 568434.0,
      "text": "After the earthquake and tsunami,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 568434.0,
      "end_time": 572221.0,
      "text": "people had to be evacuated in a big room like a gymnasium."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 572221.0,
      "end_time": 574122.0,
      "text": "But look at this. There&#39;s no privacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 574122.0,
      "end_time": 576988.0,
      "text": "People suffer mentally and physically."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 576989.0,
      "end_time": 580380.0,
      "text": "So we went there to build partitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 580380.0,
      "end_time": 583643.0,
      "text": "with all the student volunteers with paper tubes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 583643.0,
      "end_time": 587874.0,
      "text": "just a very simple shelter out of the tube frame and the curtain."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 587874.0,
      "end_time": 590390.0,
      "text": "However, some of the facility authority"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 590390.0,
      "end_time": 592437.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t want us to do it, because, they said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 592437.0,
      "end_time": 595634.0,
      "text": "simply, it&#39;s become more difficult to control them."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 595634.0,
      "end_time": 598116.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s really necessary to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 598116.0,
      "end_time": 600621.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t have enough flat area to build"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 600621.0,
      "end_time": 603906.0,
      "text": "standard government single-story housing like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 603906.0,
      "end_time": 606156.0,
      "text": "Look at this. Even civil government is doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 606156.0,
      "end_time": 610285.0,
      "text": "such poor construction of the temporary housing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 610285.0,
      "end_time": 616815.0,
      "text": "so dense and so messy because there is no storage, nothing, water is leaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 616816.0,
      "end_time": 620850.0,
      "text": "so I thought, we have to make multi-story building"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 620850.0,
      "end_time": 623110.0,
      "text": "because there&#39;s no land and also it&#39;s not very comfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 623110.0,
      "end_time": 628400.0,
      "text": "So I proposed to the mayor while I was making partitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 628400.0,
      "end_time": 631670.0,
      "text": "Finally I met a very nice mayor in Onagawa village"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 631671.0,
      "end_time": 632991.0,
      "text": "in Miyagi."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 632991.0,
      "end_time": 637377.0,
      "text": "He asked me to build three-story housing on baseball [fields]."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 637377.0,
      "end_time": 640103.0,
      "text": "I used the shipping container"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 640103.0,
      "end_time": 642555.0,
      "text": "and also the students helped us to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 642556.0,
      "end_time": 645354.0,
      "text": "all the building furniture"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 645354.0,
      "end_time": 647460.0,
      "text": "to make them comfortable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 647460.0,
      "end_time": 649321.0,
      "text": "within the budget of the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 649321.0,
      "end_time": 653230.0,
      "text": "but also the area of the house is exactly the same,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 653230.0,
      "end_time": 654370.0,
      "text": "but much more comfortable."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 654370.0,
      "end_time": 657502.0,
      "text": "Many of the people want to stay here forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 657502.0,
      "end_time": 660640.0,
      "text": "I was very happy to hear that."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 660640.0,
      "end_time": 664100.0,
      "text": "Now I am working in New Zealand, Christchurch."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 664100.0,
      "end_time": 667848.0,
      "text": "About 20 days before the Japanese earthquake happened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 667848.0,
      "end_time": 669353.0,
      "text": "also they had a big earthquake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 669353.0,
      "end_time": 671914.0,
      "text": "and many Japanese students were also killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 671914.0,
      "end_time": 674233.0,
      "text": "and the most important cathedral of the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 674233.0,
      "end_time": 677300.0,
      "text": "the symbol of Christchurch, was totally destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 677400.0,
      "end_time": 681102.0,
      "text": "And I was asked to come to rebuild the temporary cathedral."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 681102.0,
      "end_time": 683389.0,
      "text": "So this is under construction."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 683389.0,
      "end_time": 686729.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like to keep building monuments"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 686729.0,
      "end_time": 688959.0,
      "text": "that are beloved by people."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 688959.0,
      "end_time": 690397.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 690398.0,
      "end_time": 692334.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 692334.0,
      "end_time": 695660.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 695670.0,
      "end_time": 697824.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}